{
  "texts": [
    "Building on this concept, SPPNet incorporates several key advancements.",
    "Net efficiently handles images of various sizes, providing scale-invariant detection capabilities.",
    "Leveraging multi-scale features extracted from different subregions significantly improves localization accuracy and enhances overall detection performance.",
    "These features collectively make SPPNet a robust and accurate model for object detection, particularly in scenarios involving diverse image sizes and complex spatial structures.",
    "The primary limitation of R-CNN lies in its slow processing speed and high computational cost, primarily due to its dependence on selective search for region proposals."
  ]
}